Design a Paid Ad System for a Search Site

parts include:
* update to consumer UI to display ads
* ad storage
* ad matching system
* ad purchase system (including targets, by subject or demographic)
* ad login system

* update to consumer UI to display ads
	dependent on current UI implementation; different page regions, etc.
* ad storage
	needs to be very responsive; no delays.  
* ad matching system
	needs to be very responsive; no delays.  NoSQL, etc  
	purchased keywords- sharded, relatively easy
	'related' keywords need to define related.  Can build map over time (search terms-> words in clicked page)  
* ad purchase system (including targets, by subject or demographic)
	selling by keyword is easy; demographic depends on what data we have on user.
* ad login system
	generic.
